    <date year="2021" month="January" day="15"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>In case operators decide to delay BGPsec path validation, none of the available states do properly represent this decision. This document introduces "Unverified" as a well-defined validation state which allows to properly identify a non-evaluated BGPsec routes as not verified.</t>
    </abstract>
